OL,3,CMeet Fergus the school therapy dog
OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FKatie Cole has been to a primary
OL,8,Fschool in Newcastle to see how therapy
OL,9,Fdog Fergus is making a difference
OL,11,FA therapy dog is being used in
OL,12,FNewcastle to help support
OL,13,Fschoolchildren with disabilities and
OL,14,Fspecial educational needs - and to
OL,15,Fimprove attendance.
OL,17,FOne-year-old Fergus is brought into
OL,18,FWellbeck Academy, in Walker, by owner
OL,19,Fand school counsellor Heather O'Neill.
