OL,3,CMeet Fergus the school therapy dog
OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FAt a time when 90% of schools have
OL,8,Fseen a rise of pupils with special
OL,9,Feducational needs (SEND), Heather told
OL,10,FITV Tyne Tees Fergus was making a
OL,11,Fdifference.
OL,13,F"He's not what is classed as a usual
OL,14,Fschool dog that has the freedom to
OL,15,Froam around the corridors," she said.
OL,17,F"Fergus is used specifically in my
OL,18,Froom as a counselling intervention
OL,19,Fbecause dogs have been known to reduce
OL,20,Fanxiety and to reduce stress."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
