OL,3,CMeet Fergus the school therapy dog
OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FSome of the school's pupils said
OL,8,FFergus had already worked his magic on
OL,9,Fthem - making them feel happier, being
OL,10,Fa listening ear and a perfect
OL,11,Fdistraction.
OL,13,FHeather continued: "We do see children
OL,14,Fwho have got special educational
OL,15,Fneeds, so I see children with autism
OL,16,For ADHD, speech and language delay as
OL,17,Fwell, he listens and doesn't give any
OL,18,Ffeedback.
