OL,3,CMeet Fergus the school therapy dog
OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,F"They can often pour their heart out -
OL,8,FI'll see children who've lost a family
OL,9,Fmember, maybe parents have separated
OL,10,Fand they would come and just offload
OL,11,Ftheir worries."
OL,13,FAnd while Fergus has had a glowing
OL,14,Freference from staff and pupils, dog
OL,15,Ftrainer Nicola Maxwell said there was
OL,16,Fgrowing wider support for the use of
OL,17,Fdogs in schools.
