OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FNicola, from Paws Therapy Dog
OL,8,FTraining, said: "Since covid, with the
OL,9,Ffall out in terms of society's mental
OL,10,Fhealth, and the influx of children
OL,11,Fthat are coming through diagnoses of
OL,12,Fautism and ADHD, people are
OL,13,Frecognising that dogs can have a huge
OL,14,Fimpact on those people in terms of
OL,15,Fsupporting them."
OL,17,FDogs are also being used to improve
OL,18,Fattendance. Rates have fallen since
OL,19,Fthe pandemic and across the North East
OL,20,Fone in five pupils are persistently
OL,21,Fabsent.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
