OL,3,CMeet Fergus the school therapy dog
OL,4,Chelping lower anxiety and boost
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,F"We know that since covid a lot of
OL,8,Fchildren are struggling to engage in
OL,9,Fschool learning and our dogs can help
OL,10,Fthem to do that," added Nicola.
OL,12,F"Having that friendly, happy face with
OL,13,Fthe waggy tail greet them can just be
OL,14,Fthat little bit of confidence to help
OL,15,Fthem cross over the threshold."
OL,17,FOur canine friends also proven to help
OL,18,Fwith literacy skills.
