OL,7,FHeather continued: "To them, there's
OL,8,Fno criticism, there's no being told
OL,9,Fit's wrong.
OL,11,F"I think it's just giving a different
OL,12,Fdimension and a different aspect of
OL,13,Fhelping children and knowing that he
OL,14,Fmakes such a difference to them is
OL,15,Freally powerful actually."
